{"tid":1489002,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[對外文宣] 最近多咗人用Twitter宣傳香港嘅野俾世界知 但「外國勢力」有個建議俾大家","createTime":"2019-08-19T18:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T03:46:12.000Z","uid":213747,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff8176d61ce8c9b0bef912e7992585444d26a07","tid":1489002,"uid":213747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:20:19.000Z","msg":"引用Hong Kong Hermit英文tweet:<br />\n<blockquote>其實香港而家已經得到咗世界嘅關注<br />\n外國想喺twitter之類社交媒體睇到嘅係真正嘅英文(文字)<br />\n唔好再spam一大堆hashtag落去<br />\n世界想聽到嘅係你嘅聲音<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkonghermit/status/1163473428159979523?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkonghermit%2Fstatus%2F1163473428159979523%3Fs%3D21&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=06b86cf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkonghermit%2Fstatus%2F1163473428159979523%3Fs%3D21&h=66231da2\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkonghermit/status/1163473428159979523?s=21</a></blockquote><br />\n利申完全贊成 就算我地洗咗一大堆hashtag落去<br />\n就算推到<span style=\"color: blue;\">#StandwithHK</span>入咗trend <br />\n外國人見到啲hasgtag海 了解唔到件事之餘可能會反感<br />\n<br />\n如果自問英文唔好嘅話 其實打返中文都唔怕<br />\nTwitter內置嗰個翻譯系統都算唔太差<br />\n再唔係嘅話 其實有人自發幫手翻譯<br />\n只要加返<span style=\"color: blue;\">#Hongkongers</span>依個hashtag<br />\n<blockquote>To add to @HongKongHermit great thread on Twitter dos/donts: #Hongkongers it's perfectly fine to write in Cantonese/Chinese on Twitter if you aren't comfy w/English to express thoughts&amp;feelings. We bilingual ppl can happily turn your tweets➡️English 💪</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/mandyleedubhkg/status/1163476762040385536?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmandyleedubhkg%2Fstatus%2F1163476762040385536%3Fs%3D21&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex%2BgMmE0tIaoAQI%2BAeX1JER4%3D&h=aa4ae564\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmandyleedubhkg%2Fstatus%2F1163476762040385536%3Fs%3D21&h=fa055aaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/mandyleedubhkg/status/1163476762040385536?s=21</a><br />\n我都會幫手翻譯吓 各位手足繼續加油<br />\n俾世界了解我地嘅實際情況 爭取更多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f14216d94dcd5cb00bb031a51b6b36b0818a3db","tid":1489002,"uid":290804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:21:52.000Z","msg":"&lt;821&gt;咁撚大件事冇人講 全撚同我入嚟！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488892</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2ed9408051bc2a06ac0472bc00f26c37173c357b","tid":1489002,"uid":270871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:22:30.000Z","msg":"推，社交網站係用嚟講人話<br />\n唔係用嚟洗版架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16eb728e14c6c95755bc8d0576f54c904e82ba56","tid":1489002,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:24:09.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13cbca9c2b1abf3de27a0d69f118ba07ee7c40a9","tid":1489002,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T18:26:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">824和理非自發出機場</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">錫政府春袋 癱瘓機場貨運</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">機鐵會有阻塞運動<br />\n需要車手去機場塞路<br />\n亦可以排隊入機場</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">記住善待遊客 盡幫佢地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTQBGjH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTQBGjH.jpg&h=a4cec47b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7FesZ